{"tid":992790,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟驚自己唔再鍾意一個人係因為愛佢定唔夠愛佢","createTime":"2019-01-23T12:22:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T14:49:19.000Z","uid":231397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"92aa101e4b177a59d0a06095bfbdcf0f921eb6d0","tid":992790,"uid":231397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T12:22:17.000Z","msg":"我的確好想同佢一直喺埋一齊<br />\n但同時我會成日擔心/想像將來有咩意外令我唔再鍾意佢<br />\n例如變冷淡左或者鍾意左第二個<br />\n究竟係因為我太愛佢唔想失去佢<br />\n定係因為我冇信心足夠愛佢<br />\n我自己都搞唔清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"528c0e138fac7671894034f5df2928a8e3c8c271","tid":992790,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T12:55:44.000Z","msg":"是但啦"},{"pid":"99fe4ca6d71122bf7c0e400483345ee11f4ad99d","tid":992790,"uid":206812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T14:49:19.000Z","msg":"我對上一次有呢個諗法係一年前<br />\n當時我同前男友已經一齊咗四年 有呢個諗法之後無幾耐就分咗手<br />\n我知道 我係唔夠愛佢<br />\n而最後 我戴左頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}